 research staff and the (quality of being connected or related to something) of its research program. The fourth factor adding/giving to the growth of NARS is the lack of institutional (machines/methods/ways) to 
 finance (related to a large area) research institutes. 11 As a result, there is (making copies of something/more than one person doing the same thing) of 
